casebody.data:
Walter BARTON, Petitioner,
v.
William STANGE, Warden. No. 19-8483
19A1040 Supreme Court of the United States. May 19, 2020

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice Gorsuch and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
